Hence from Fig\ref{fig:ee18btech110026_circuit_2} 
\begin{align}
H(s) = \frac{V_{f}}{V_{0}}
	&= \frac{1}{1+sR_{f}C_{f}}
\end{align}

The loop gain of the compensated system is :
\begin{align}
G(s)H(s) = \frac{10^{4}}{(1+sR_{f}C_{f})(1+\frac{s}{P_{1}})(1+\frac{s}{P_{2}})(1+\frac{s}{P_{3}})}
\end{align}

