\item {\textbf{What is the practical use of the built circuit ?}}
\solution
The Bode plot of the closed loop T.F is as follows:
\begin{align}
T(s) = \frac{G(s)}{1+G(s)H(s)}
\end{align}
\begin{figure}[!h]
    \centering
    \includegraphics[width=\columnwidth]{./figs/ee18btech11026/Bodeplot.eps}
