\end{figure}
\\From Fig:\ref{fig:ee18btech11026_bode} we can say that this circuit is used as \textbf{Band pass filter}. It amplifies the frequencies lying between 0.1 MHz to 10 MHz, while rejecting higher and lower frequencies.
